# The website Dockerfile builds the Astro site from the repo-root build context
# (Railway default). Narrow that context to website/ so the monorepo isn't sent
# to the builder. scripts/ralph/Dockerfile is a codex dev image that COPYs
# nothing from the repo, so this doesn't affect it.
#
# The website build's docs:gen:ts (typedoc) step also needs the agentos SDK
# source, which lives outside website/. Include just that package's src + config
# (not node_modules/dist) so the API reference can be generated in the image.
*
!website
!packages
packages/*
!packages/agentos
packages/agentos/*
!packages/agentos/src
!packages/agentos/package.json
!packages/agentos/tsconfig.json
website/node_modules
website/dist
website/.astro

# The docs <CodeSnippet> embeds read example source from /examples (the embed
# root is the parent of the website). Include the example source only — never
# their node_modules/dist/build output.
!examples
examples/**/node_modules
examples/**/dist
examples/**/.astro
examples/**/.turbo
